                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="fw-bold" style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: #1E3A8A; line-height: 1; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">0</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #64748B; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; margin-top: 6px; white-space: nowrap;">/ 1,500 words per day</div>
