                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748B; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">- Zig Ziglar</p>
                
                <div class="text-end mt-auto">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-1" style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #94A3B8; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; transition: color 0.2s;">
